{"tid":1509880,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"致狗狗們的信！ 係我就check 下另一半有冇帽你","createTime":"2019-08-27T03:40:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T08:48:15.000Z","uid":13903,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"be5bb50c3f959e5fd516eac1f4d68dc3b23755b2","tid":1509880,"uid":13903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T03:40:03.000Z","msg":"致 犬氏家庭 ： <br />\n<br />\n由於近日瘋狗症蔓延全港，在全港多區失去控制，更與畜氏龍咬傷多名市民。<br />\n而最近更有消息指犬氏拖人類到邊界地區行使私刑，更對其下施非禮之刑。<br />\n由此，請各大犬氏家庭記緊時常檢查對方是否有超越道德之嫌 ，<br />\n並時常督促另一半有否出軌之行為。<br />\n若對確認屬實，不妨閹割或私下人道毀滅，以促進文明社會發展和自然反應之舉動。<br />\n<br />\n祝<br />\n花開富貴，連生貴子<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n婚姻關係輔導<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://family.caritas.org.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffamily.caritas.org.hk&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrnHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=e4084da8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://family.caritas.org.hk</a>  [/url]<br />\n<br />\n性傳染疾病- 香港家庭計劃指導會<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.famplan.org.hk/zh/health-info/sexually-transmissible-diseases\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.famplan.org.hk%2Fzh%2Fhealth-info%2Fsexually-transmissible-diseases&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrnHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=6e9c33c8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.famplan.org.hk/zh/health-info/sexually-transmissible-diseases</a><br />\n<br />\n香港愛護動物協會<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.spca.org.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.spca.org.hk&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrnHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=6ffe32c8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.spca.org.hk</a><br />\n<br />\n閹割刀組合<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.1688.com/chanpin/-.html?[url]spm=a261b.2187593.searchbar.2.oUjRZK&amp;keywords=%E9%8E%B8%EE[/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.1688.com%2Fchanpin%2F-.html%3F%5Burl%5Dspm%3Da261b.2187593.searchbar.2.oUjRZK%26keywords%3D%25E9%258E%25B8%25EE%5B%2Furl%5D&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrnHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=1a006414\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">h